snippet.title: DCCOR Drawing
snippet.description:
About DCCOR
 
Welcome to my channel (__a

This is a channel that shows the drawing process using various art tools!

Draw and draw other drawings or messages in it.

We try to upload as much quality and interesting video as possible.

Your interest and support is a great strength for me @. @

Subscribe ♥ Like ♥ Pretty comments ♥ Share ♥ is my driving force !!
 
Thank you for watching and we will reward you with a good video!

Have a nice day!!


Material used:

Colored Pencils [Plasma]
Pastel [Farber, Stabilo]
Alpha Watercolor Color
Uniposka
Maca [Copic]
